    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ℹ️ This demo is a <strong>rolling snapshot</strong> of our current progress on Spellsided. That means with each <strong>fortnightly update</strong> you’ll often see new spells, enemies, mechanics, improvements, tweaks and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being an actively in-development build however, the &quot;and more&quot; part sometimes (usually) includes some <strong>funky bugs</strong> and <strong>performance issues</strong>. If you have a problem with the game the best place to get help is on our Discord server, which you can find in the sidebar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195080/extras/cbba0fa146290bf3e65e65d41e6ae6b3.avif?t=1769871043\" width=1170 height=192 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your shape rotation skills and compete with the community with <strong>regular puzzle releases</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195080/extras/96bfca7e298f99376870a7eec940294a.poster.avif?t=1769871043\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195080/extras/96bfca7e298f99376870a7eec940294a.webm?t=1769871043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195080/extras/96bfca7e298f99376870a7eec940294a.mp4?t=1769871043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>@merijn2018’s 26-move solution for Challenge #3</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share your fastest, funniest, and most interesting solutions on our Discord leaderboards. We might even highlight your best solutions on YouTube, if you can break the game in ways we didn’t expect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195080/extras/5343a8c9181b8b20b61ceab8a7a6afcf.avif?t=1769871043\" width=1024 height=806 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The <strong>Domino Den </strong>campaign has been archived on a beta branch, which you can access in the game’s properties menu in the Steam library. It’ll return in the future in a much improved state!</i></p>",
